Cohesity Backup Failures Workflow

Cohesity Cluster Capacity and Garbage Collection Workflow
Cohesity Long-Running Backup Workflow
Dynatrace workflow monitors backup and replication protection groups across all Cohesity clusters and identifies runs exceeding 24 hours. It captures protection group–level details and executes twice daily at 09:00 and 22:00, listing only long-running protection groups to highlight potential delays or stuck activity.
